lyrics:
[Verse]
Blossoms in a barren land, vibrant and rare
Skeleton men wander, their souls stripped bare
Endless ticking, time dripping in every way
Empty hours drag on, like a neverending play

[Chorus]
Clock mindless, monotonous day
Searching for something to do, find a way
Clock mindless, monotonous day
Yearning for purpose, longing to break away
style: a "Turkish Rap" in the "Gucci Gang" style
